Track name: Long Pond Superspeedway

Based on Pocono Raceway, Long Pond, Pennsylvania.
A superspeedway in the Pocono Mountains of Pennsylvania at Long Pond,
opened in 1974.

Credits:
-Haruna Say for the idea of more speedways in Speed Dreams

